quran[12]{c,v,t}:
  67,1,BLESSED be He is whose hand is the KINGDOM! and over all things is He potent
  67,2,"Who hath created death and life to prove which of you will be most righteous in deed; and He is the Mighty, the Forgiving"
  67,3,"Who hath created seven Heavens one above another: No defect canst thou see in the creation of the God of Mercy: Repeat the gaze: seest thou a single flaw"
  67,4,"Then twice more repeat the gaze: thy gaze shall return to thee dulled and weary"
  67,5,"Moreover we have decked the lowest heaven with lights, and have placed them there to be hurled at the Satans, for whom we have prepared the torment of the flaming fire"
  67,6,And for those who believe not in their Lord is the torment of Hell; and horrid the journey thither
  67,7,"When they shall be thrown into it, they shall hear it braying: and it shall boil"
  67,8,"Almost shall it burst for fury. So oft as a crowd shall be thrown into it, its keepers shall ask them, \"Came not the warner to you"
  67,9,"They shall say, Yes! there came to us one charged with warnings; but we treated him as a liar, and said, \"Nothing hath God sent down: ye are in nothing but a vast delusion"
  67,10,"And they shall say, \"Had we but hearkened or understood, we had not been among the dwellers in the flames"
  67,11,"And their sin shall they acknowledge: but, \"Avaunt, ye dwellers in the flame"
  67,12,But pardon and a great reward for those who fear their Lord in secret